[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Notification System
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] The notification system sends transactional emails via SendGrid for bug lifecycle events and auth flows.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Architecture
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] Bug/Auth Event
[CLAUDE]      │
[CLAUDE] BugNotificationEventService   ← records event
[CLAUDE]      │
[CLAUDE] NotificationDispatcher        ← fan-out to recipients
[CLAUDE]      │
[CLAUDE] BugRecipientService           ← determines who gets notified
[CLAUDE]      │
[CLAUDE] SendGridDelivery              ← sends email via SendGrid API
[CLAUDE]      │
[CLAUDE] NotificationStore             ← persists delivery record
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Event Types
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Bug-related events that trigger notifications:
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Event | Template |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Bug created | `bug-created.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Bug assigned | `bug-assigned.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Bug status changed | `bug-status-changed.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Bug comment added | `bug-comment.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Bug closed | `bug-closed.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Bug reopened | `bug-reopened.html` |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Auth-related emails:
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Purpose | Template |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Email verification | `verification.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Welcome | `welcome.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Forgot password | `forgot-password.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Password reset complete | `password-reset-complete.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Password changed | `password-changed.html` |
[CLAUDE] | Organization invitation | `organization-invitation.html` |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] All templates extend `base-layout.html`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Template Engine
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/notifications/template-engine.ts` — simple variable substitution engine for HTML email templates. Templates live in `src/lib/notifications/templates/`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Notification Settings
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Per-organization settings control which event types are enabled for which recipient groups. Managed via:
[CLAUDE] - Admin UI: `/admin/notifications`
[CLAUDE] - API: `PATCH /api/admin/notifications/settings`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Retry Mechanism
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Failed deliveries and events can be retried via admin API:
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/notifications/deliveries/[deliveryId]/retry`
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/notifications/events/[eventId]/retry`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Local Development
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Leave `SENDGRID_API_KEY` empty to disable email delivery locally. The notification flow still runs; deliveries are recorded as skipped/failed in the database.
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
[CLAUDE] 
